[ctns_make id='gen_abs_prop_pm_c']

  [ctns_front style='font-size:150%;']
$$|x| = c$$
  [/ctns_front]  

  [ctns_back style='font-size:100%;']
$||x| = c|$ is equivalent to $|x = \pm c|$
  [/ctns_back]  

  [ctns_frontspeak]
The absolute value of x -- equals -- a constant -- c.
  [/ctns_frontspeak]  

  [ctns_backspeak]
When the absolute value of x -- equals -- a constant -- c,  then the value of x -- equals -- plus or minus the constant c.
  [/ctns_backspeak]  

[/ctns_make]
